'''''Saattai Illatha Pambaram''''' is a [[1983 in film|1983]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by Erode N.Murugesh for Punitha Cine Arts. The film stars [[Sivakumar]] and [[Saritha]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Saattai Illatha Pambaram LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/148/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-02|}}</ref>

